<Chapter id="Chapter.ErrorFormatters">
  <Title/System Error Formatters: <<ErrorFormatters>>/
  <P>
    This module provides a set of formatters for system componeents.
    These formatters are registered by the <<Error>> module.  The system
    components handled by this module are the following:
    <List>
      <Entry/<<kernel>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<kernel>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from Kernel Oz,
	such as type errors.
      <Entry/<<object>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<object>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from the object
	system, &eg;, inheritance errors.
      <Entry/<<failure>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<failure>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions pertaining to failure
	(&ie;, inconsistent <Q/tell/ operations on the store).
      <Entry/<<recordC>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<recordC>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from the feature
	constraint system.
      <Entry/<<system>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<system>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from libraries
	used for system programming.
      <Entry/<<ap>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<ap>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from libraries
	used for application programming.
      <Entry/<<dp>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<dp>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from libraries
	used for distributed programming.
      <Entry/<<os>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<os>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from the operating
	system interface.
      <Entry/<<foreign>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<foreign>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from foreign function
	interface.
      <Entry/<<url>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<url>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from the URL resolving
	library.
      <Entry/<<module>>
	<Index class=tails/<<ErrorFormatters>><And><<module>>//
      <Item>
	is an error formatter for exceptions coming from the module manager.
    </List>
</Chapter>
